Daivdnya Brahmin also popularly known as daivadnya sonar. This cast is predominantly found in Maharashtra, Goa and Karnataka. The cast is refered so, because these people were wellversed in knowing astrology and could predict future by studying positions of stars petaining to the specific person. Later on this profession was slipped from their hands and the daivadnyas came into art profession. One of the art is of gold smith. that is why they are popular by sonar as a cast.